  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Moth is a first person thriller where you play as a police investigator searching the underground parking hall for a murderer. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you descend deeper underground, you find out that absolutely nothing is what it seems. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What has really happened? What is the true crime?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your way out of the nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3625420/extras/6243f8485538991bd08ed16c4e0b9bfe.avif?t=1744660983\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3625420/extras_big/6243f8485538991bd08ed16c4e0b9bfe.avif?t=1744660983 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UNIQUE ENVIRONMENT: </strong>search the underground parking hall with six levels for clues. Every level brings a twist to the story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NO SAVE GAME:</strong> you have to play until the end. About 1 hour of gameplay without any save games, to really capture the story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>IMMERSIVE: </strong>Realistic graphics + british voice acting along with minimalistic UI for a  immersive player experience.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Moth is a first person thriller where you play as a police investigator searching the underground parking hall for a murderer. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you descend deeper underground, you find out that absolutely nothing is what it seems. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What has really happened? What is the true crime?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your way out of the nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3625420/extras/6243f8485538991bd08ed16c4e0b9bfe.avif?t=1744660983\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3625420/extras_big/6243f8485538991bd08ed16c4e0b9bfe.avif?t=1744660983 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UNIQUE ENVIRONMENT: </strong>search the underground parking hall with six levels for clues. Every level brings a twist to the story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NO SAVE GAME:</strong> you have to play until the end. About 1 hour of gameplay without any save games, to really capture the story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>IMMERSIVE: </strong>Realistic graphics + british voice acting along with minimalistic UI for a  immersive player experience.</p></li></ul>",
